comments[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-23T04:54:32.200Z",codex-root,Duplicate-safe searches found adjacent closed lineage but no existing typed validate_config or hard-coded candidate-version regression item.
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-23T04:54:32.200Z",codex-root,"Never store live automation contents,entity inventories,tokens,user IDs,signed paths,or raw server responses in tracker or repository evidence."
learnings[1]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-23T04:54:32.200Z",codex-root,Home Assistant 2026.4.4 and current Core source require plural validate_config keys even though the rendered API docs currently describe singular labels.
